OL,3,CJudgement reserved in murder trial of
OL,4,Cjournalist Lyra McKee
OL,6,FAlmost two years after it started,
OL,7,Fjudgement was reserved on Thursday in
OL,8,Fa non-jury trial in the death of
OL,9,Fjournalist Lyra McKee.
OL,11,FThe 29-year old died after being
OL,12,Fstruck in the head by a bullet fired
OL,13,Fat police Land Rovers parked in the
OL,14,FFanad Drive area of Creggan during
OL,15,Fserious unrest on April 18, 2019.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776445554
OL,3,CJudgement reserved in murder trial of
OL,4,Cjournalist Lyra McKee
OL,6,FIn closing submissions on behalf of
OL,7,Fthe defence which marked the final
OL,8,Fstages of the trial, Mrs Justice Smith
OL,9,Fsaid she was "very grateful" to all
OL,10,Fcounsel involved in what she described
OL,11,Fas "an enormously difficult case."
OL,13,FThe senior judge said: "This has been
OL,14,Fa very complex case and as anyone who
OL,15,Fhas listened to the final submissions
OL,16,Fwill know, there are a number of
OL,17,Fperspectives that have to considered
OL,18,Fin respect of each of the important
OL,19,Fstrands of evidence in this case.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776445554
OL,3,CJudgement reserved in murder trial of
OL,4,Cjournalist Lyra McKee
OL,6,F"It's also important to note that each
OL,7,Fof the defendants is entitled to be
OL,8,Ftreated separately.
OL,10,F"Each offence with which they are
OL,11,Fcharged has to be considered
OL,12,Fseparately and for that reason I can't
OL,13,Fgive a date at this stage for the
OL,14,Ffinal judgement.
OL,16,F"It will take me some time to give
OL,17,Fproper consideration to all of the
OL,18,Fpoints that have been made in this
OL,19,Fcase - but this case will have my
OL,20,Fpriority."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
